ax-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /> <img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1089469" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-07-下午 6.08.17.png" alt="" width="482" height="264" /></p></p><div class="feedflare">
<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=NQE9rC46lXU:TBspPAPXxxY:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=NQE9rC46lXU:TBspPAPXxxY:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></img></a>
</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>郭明錤：今年不會有新 Mac Pro、iMac Pro    或只會有 M2 版 Mac mini</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/03/07/mac-pro/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=mac-pro</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[EMMA]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Mon, 07 Mar 2022 10:40:42 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1089412</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>知名 Apple 產品的分析師郭明錤於 Twitter 發表推文表示，Apple 將於 2023 年推出全新 M [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>知名 Apple 產品的分析師郭明錤於 Twitter 發表推文表示，Apple 將於 2023 年推出全新 Mac Pro 和 iMac Pro，並於今年推出更強大的 Mac mini 和 27 吋 iMac，但其螢幕並未採用 mini-LED。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">Predictions for Apple&#39;s new desktop products:<br />1. 2022: More powerful Mac mini and more affordable external display (27-inch without mini-LED).<br />2. 2023: Mac Pro and iMac Pro.</p><p>&mdash; 郭明錤 (Ming-Chi Kuo) (@mingchikuo) <a href="https://twitter.com/mingchikuo/status/1500507564148400128?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">March 6, 2022</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>郭明錤預計 Mac mini 將有一個全新的外貌設計，包括聚碳酸酯的機頂、更薄的外殼，以及強制性的內部升級，可能會使用 M1 Pro 或 M1 Max 晶片系列，以及引入 M2 晶片。</p><p>曾有傳 27 吋的 iMac 將配備 mini LED 顯示螢幕，但據郭明錤的推測，iMac 仍然配備了傳統的 LCD 螢幕，但亮度相比前一代提升了 30-40%，預計採用與 24 吋機型類似的多配色設計。</p><p>郭明錤並沒有明確提及新款 Mac Mini 會於美國時間 3 月 8 日上午 10 時舉行的春季網上發布會「Peek Performance」推出，但《彭博社》記者 Mark Gurman 曾透露，屆時將推出具 5G 功能的廉價版 iPhone SE 3、新款 iPad Air 與採用 Apple 晶片的新 Mac。</p><p class="p1"><span class="s1">資料</span><span class="s2">來源：<a href="https://www.macrumors.com/2022/03/06/kuo-imac-pro-in-2023-27-inch-display-this-year/">macrumors</a></span></p><p class="p2">—</p><p class="p2"><span class="s3">unwire.hk</span> Mewe <span class="s4">專頁：</span> <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><span class="s3">https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</span></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=IWA9wbeCMS8:Mt4dErEKisg:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=IWA9wbeCMS8:Mt4dErEKisg:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></img></a>
</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>MSI 新 AiO 一體式桌上電腦，一開即用極方便 </title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/03/07/msiaio/notebook/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=msiaio</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Lawton]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Mon, 07 Mar 2022 09:58:39 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[流動電腦]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1089419</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>MSI 推出全新 AiO (All-in-One) 一體式電腦系列，適合在家辦公，希望有一部簡單、慳位，又易用 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span lang="EN-US">MSI </span><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif;">推出全新</span><span lang="EN-US"> AiO (All-in-One) </span><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif;">一體式電腦系列，適合在家辦公，希望有一部簡單、慳位，又易用電腦的用家。當用家想添置一台電腦時，不需要再為購買不同電腦零組件及顯示器而煩惱，只需購買一台</span> <span lang="EN-US">MSI AiO </span><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif;">電腦，即可立即開始使用。</span></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/kv-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1089420" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/kv-694x289.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="289" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/kv-694x289.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/kv-1280x533.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/kv-768x320.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/kv-1536x640.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/kv-2048x853.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/kv-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><span lang="EN-US">▲MSI AiO </span><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif;">電腦共推出</span> <span lang="EN-US">2 </span><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif;">款型號，</span><span lang="EN-US">PRO AP241 11M </span><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif;">及</span><span lang="EN-US"> Modern AM271 11M</span><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif;">，為不同需要的用家提供易用又流暢的文書工作體驗</span></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/less-blue-light.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1089421" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/less-blue-light-694x567.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="567" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/less-blue-light-694x567.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/less-blue-light-768x627.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/less-blue-light.jpg 959w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif;">作為專為文書辦公而設的電腦，兩款</span> <span lang="EN-US">MSI AiO </span><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif;">電腦的螢幕皆配備</span> <span lang="EN-US">IPS </span><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif;">等級面板，具有</span><span lang="EN-US"> 178 </span><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif;">度垂直和水平寬視角，以及更佳的屏幕色彩和亮度。</span></p><p><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif;">而且</span><span lang="EN-US"> MSI </span><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif;">更加入獨家的護眼技術，同時將防閃爍、減藍光、防眩光</span> <span lang="EN-US">3 </span><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif;">項技術應用於</span> <span lang="EN-US">MSI AiO </span><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif;">電腦內置的螢幕上。盡管用家長時間使用</span><span lang="EN-US"> MSI AiO </span><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif;">電腦，也不用擔心因藍光及螢幕閃爍所導致的眼睛疲勞，令用家長時間工作時可以更集中，從而提升工作效率。</span></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/life-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1089422" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/life-694x415.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="415" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/life-694x415.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/life-1280x765.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/life-768x459.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/life-1536x918.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/life-2048x1224.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/life-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif;">硬件配置方面，兩款型號皆採用第</span><span lang="EN-US"> 11 </span><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif;">代</span><span lang="EN-US"> Intel Core I5 </span><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif;">四核芯或六核芯處理器，確保用家於工作及娛樂時都能擁有流暢及穩定的使用體驗。當中</span><span lang="EN-US"> Modern AM271 </span><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif;">更採用</span><span lang="EN-US"> Intel Iris Xe Graphics </span><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif;">進階繪圖處理器，讓用家執行圖像處理程式時，例如相片及影片編輯的應用程式，更快速及流暢，工作時更加得心應手。</span></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/0145cdc3_PRO-AP241-11M-Photo_3D3-BK.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1089423" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/0145cdc3_PRO-AP241-11M-Photo_3D3-BK-484x580.png" alt="" width="484" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/0145cdc3_PRO-AP241-11M-Photo_3D3-BK-484x580.png 484w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/0145cdc3_PRO-AP241-11M-Photo_3D3-BK-751x900.png 751w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/0145cdc3_PRO-AP241-11M-Photo_3D3-BK-768x920.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/0145cdc3_PRO-AP241-11M-Photo_3D3-BK-1282x1536.png 1282w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/0145cdc3_PRO-AP241-11M-Photo_3D3-BK-1710x2048.png 1710w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/0145cdc3_PRO-AP241-11M-Photo_3D3-BK.png 1336w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 484px" /></a></p><p><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif;">為方便需要立即使用電腦的用家，以上兩款</span><span lang="EN-US"> MSI AiO </span><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif;">一體式電腦亦於出廠時預載 </span><span lang="EN-US">Windows 11 Home</span><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif;">，於首次啟動後會立即執行設定，讓用家不用額外購買及安裝作業系統即可立即使用。</span></p><p><span lang="EN-US"> </span></p><p><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif;">對在家工作的朋友來說，無線連接相當重要。兩款</span><span lang="EN-US"> AiO </span><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif;">一體式電腦同時內置</span> <span lang="EN-US">Wi-Fi 6 </span><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif;">無線網絡及第</span><span lang="EN-US"> 5 </span><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif;">代藍牙晶片，讓用家高速及穩定地連接家中的多項設備，同時亦使</span> <span lang="EN-US">MSI AiO </span><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif;">電腦的擺放位置更具彈性。另外兩款 </span><span lang="EN-US">MSI AiO </span><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif;">電腦更於背面內置立體聲喇叭，為使用者節省擺放喇叭的空間。</span></p><p><span lang="EN-US"> </span></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/7a4d5844_Modern_AM271-Photo-2D1-BK.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1089424" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/7a4d5844_Modern_AM271-Photo-2D1-BK-694x504.png" alt="" width="694" height="504" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/7a4d5844_Modern_AM271-Photo-2D1-BK-694x504.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/7a4d5844_Modern_AM271-Photo-2D1-BK-768x558.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/7a4d5844_Modern_AM271-Photo-2D1-BK.png 1126w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif;">除此之外，高階型號</span><span lang="EN-US"> Modern AM271 </span><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif;">更額外配備多項進階功能，令使用體驗更上一層樓。</span></p><p><span lang="EN-US"> </span></p><h2><b><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif;">硬碟</span></b><b><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif;">快速升級維護設計</span></b></h2><p><span lang="EN-US">Modern AM271 </span><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif;">特別於機身側面設置能夠輕易打開的</span> <span lang="EN-US">2.5 </span><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif;">吋硬碟插槽。當用家需要升級儲存空間時，只需打開側面的保護蓋就能安裝</span> <span lang="EN-US">2.5 </span><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif;">吋硬碟</span><span lang="EN-US">/SSD</span><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif;">。</span></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/aippt0007.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1089425" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/aippt0007-657x580.jpg" alt="" width="657" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/aippt0007-657x580.jpg 657w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/aippt0007-1019x900.jpg 1019w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/aippt0007-768x678.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/aippt0007.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 657px" /></a></p><h2><b><span lang="EN-US">Instant Display (HDMI-in </span></b><b><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif;">輸入插口</span></b><b><span lang="EN-US">)</span></b></h2><p><span lang="EN-US">Modern AM271 </span><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif;">除了</span><span lang="EN-US"> HDMI-out </span><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif;">輸出插口外，更特別添加</span><span lang="EN-US"> HDMI-in </span><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif;">輸入插口，讓用家可以把它當作螢幕使用，連接家中的藍光影碟機或遊戲主機。只需一台</span><span lang="EN-US"> Modern AM271</span><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif;">，即可兼顧辦公及娛樂。</span></p><p><span lang="EN-US"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/aippt0006.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1089426" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/aippt0006-548x580.png" alt="" width="548" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/aippt0006-548x580.png 548w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/aippt0006-850x900.png 850w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/aippt0006-768x813.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/aippt0006.png 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 548px" /></a></span></p><p><span lang="EN-US"> </span></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/aippt0003.jpg"> </a></p><h2><b><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif;">支援 </span></b><b><span lang="EN-US">VESA </span></b><b><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif;">掛架</span></b><b></b></h2><p><span lang="EN-US">Modern AM271 </span><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif;">額外提供標準的 </span><span lang="EN-US">VESA </span><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif;">壁掛孔</span> <span lang="EN-US">(75x75mm)</span><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif;">，可隨您的需求輕鬆安裝於辦公室或家中任何角落的牆面。</span></p><p><span lang="EN-US"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/aippt0003.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1089427" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/aippt0003-694x370.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="370" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/aippt0003-694x370.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/aippt0003-768x409.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/aippt0003.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></span></p><p><span lang="EN-US"> </span></p><p><span lang="EN-US">MSI AiO </span><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif;">一體式電腦</span><span lang="EN-US"> PRO AP241 11M </span><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif;">及</span><span lang="EN-US"> Modern AM271 11M </span><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif;">已於即日起發售，建議零售價分別為</span><span lang="EN-US"> HK$6,999 </span><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif;">及</span> <span lang="EN-US">HK$8,999</span><span style="font-family: 新細明體, serif;">。</span></p><p><span lang="ZH-HK" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif;">查詢：漢科</span><span lang="ZH-HK"> </span><span lang="EN-US">(</span><span lang="EN-US">3626 9899</span><span lang="EN-US">)</span></p><p><span lang="EN-US"> </span></p><p><b><span lang="EN-US">MSI</span></b><b><span lang="EN-US"> AiO </span></b><b><span lang="ZH-HK" style="font-family: 新細明體, serif;">一體式電腦</span></b><b><span lang="ZH-HK"> </span></b><b><span lang="EN-US">PRO AP241 11M</